high_descs: Turn to the right and walk across the room, then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and take out the apple that is on a shelf.
Turn to the right and walk across the room, then turn left.
Open the microwave and put the apple inside, then turn on the microwave for three seconds, then open the microwave and take the apple.
Turn around and take one step, then turn right and walk to the fridge, then turn right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the apple inside.
Turn right, go to the coffee machine on the counter, turn right, move to the fridge across the room.
Pick up the apple in the fridge.
Bring the apple to the mike in the corner to your right.
Heat the apple in the mike.
Take the heated apple back to the fridge on your left.
Put the heated apple in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk around the island to the fridge.
Get an apple from the fridge.
Walk to the microwave on your left.
Put the apple in the microwave and remove it.
Walk back to the fridge on your right.
Put the apple in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Warm an apple to chill again.
